content.p: The ESE team consists of a central faculty team based in the Faculty of Science Hub and a number of school-based ESE Senior Administrators. The Faculty ESE Team aim to deliver the best possible student experience by working with and supporting colleagues across all seven schools and Natural Sciences in line with our university and faculty ESE Strategic Plans. Here you will find more information about members of the team, what we do and what are plans are for the future. Watch this space for some exciting work happening in the Science ESE team!
